{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/ekshibisi-naobun-project-agensi-komik/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Ekshibisi NaoBun Project Pamerkan Komik Hingga Instalasi Seni","content":"<p>Semakin berkembangnya skena komik Indonesia dari segi karya, tentunya harus didukung dengan perkembangan dari segi industrinya. Dengan memperhatikan alasan tersebut, berbagai agensi yang bertujuan menghubungkan kreator dengan industri pun bermunculan. <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/diskusi-seru-di-japan-foundation-bareng-nao-bun-project/\">NaoBun Project</a> memiliki misi yang sama, yaitu membangun industri komik Indonesia dengan mengembangkan skill kreator dan menghubungkan mereka dengan industri komik Indonesia.</p>\n<p>“Dengan belajar dari Jepang, kami bertujuan besar membangun ekosistem industri karakter yang kuat di dalam dan luar negeri,” ungkap <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/mengenal-bonni-rambatan-sosok-di-balik-primate-peril/\">Bonni Rambatan</a>, <em>founder</em> dari NaoBun Project. Bonni mendirikan NaoBun Project bersama dengan Naomi Saddhadhika, yang mana NaoBun sendiri merupakan subsidiari dari <a href=\"http://rambatansaddhadhika.co.id/\">Rambatan Saddhadhika Design Firm</a>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46969\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46969\" data-attachment-id=\"46969\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ekshibisi-naobun-project-agensi-komik/attachment/01-naobun-project/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-naobun-project.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-naobun-project\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-naobun-project-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-naobun-project.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46969\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-naobun-project.jpg\" alt=\"01 naobun project\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-naobun-project.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-naobun-project-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46969\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Sebagai bukti sumbangsihnya, NaoBun Project menggelar sebuah ekshibisi bertajuk We Are NaoBun Project. Ekshibisi ini menampilkan 13 karya yang diproduksi dengan bantuan NaoBun Project dan disalurkan ke berbagai jenis <em>platform</em>. Ekshibisi ini berlangsung dari tanggal 6 sampai 13 Mei 2018 di The Japan Foundation Jakarta.</p>\n<p>Karya-karya yang ditampilkan memiliki berbagai jenis format dan sarana publikasinya sendiri. Misalnya ada komik <em>cult hit</em> Mera Puti Emas yang sudah turun cetak, <em>webtoon</em> Sofia Fashion Investigations dengan tampilan <em>all-new</em>-nya, Primate Peril yang bisa kamu baca langsung <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/primate-peril\">di CIAYO Comics</a>, dan masih banyak lagi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46970\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46970\" data-attachment-id=\"46970\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ekshibisi-naobun-project-agensi-komik/attachment/02-naobun-project/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-naobun-project.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-naobun-project\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-naobun-project-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-naobun-project.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46970\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-naobun-project.jpg\" alt=\"02-naobun-project\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-naobun-project.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-naobun-project-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46970\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Karya-karya yang lahir dari NaoBun Project juga senantiasa mengangkat tema yang unik. Misalnya saja dalam komik Das Sollen yang mengangkat kisah drama hukum bertema industri kreatif, atau Wrench in the Works dimana sekelompok cewek “mencuri” alat perubahan milik tim <em>magical girl</em>. Ada pula karya-karya yang mengulas sisi depresif seperti Liyan 119.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46971\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46971\" data-attachment-id=\"46971\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ekshibisi-naobun-project-agensi-komik/attachment/03-naobun-project/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-naobun-project.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-naobun-project\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-naobun-project-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-naobun-project.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46971\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-naobun-project.jpg\" alt=\"03-naobun-project\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-naobun-project.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-naobun-project-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46971\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>NaoBun Project juga menelurkan karya-karya multimedia lewat medium yang tidak konvensional. Misalnya ada Bunny dan Nao, komik yang mengaplikasikan elemen <em>puzzle</em> interaktif dan permainan kartu <em>escape the room</em>. Lain lagi dengan Sailor Spica, yang menggabungkan musik dengan instalasi seni.</p>\n<p>Meski memiliki berbagai macam tema, bentuk, dan cara pemyampaian, karya-karya dari NaoBun Project selalu memiliki satu benang merah: mengangkat isu penting. “Komik yang baik adalah komik yang mampu mengangkat isu-isu sosial yang relevan dari lingkungan sekitarnya,” terang Bonni.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46972\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46972\" data-attachment-id=\"46972\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ekshibisi-naobun-project-agensi-komik/attachment/04-naobun-project/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-naobun-project.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-naobun-project\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-naobun-project-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-naobun-project.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46972\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-naobun-project.jpg\" alt=\"04-naobun-project\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-naobun-project.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-naobun-project-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46972\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Menurut Bonni sendiri, untuk mencapai tujuan itu, sebuah komik tak perlu terlalu menggurui dan memberikan pesan moralnya secara gamblang. “Namun, komik yang baik selalu mengangkat tema-tema yang relevan untuk memberikan argumen cerita yang baik, disertai dengan desain yang layak dan riset yang bisa dipertanggungjawabkan,” tambahnya.</p>\n<p>Untuk itu, judul-judul yang ditangani NaoBun Project senantiasa merangkul berbagai organisasi dan LSM sebagai penasihat atau mitra riset. Misalnya saja dalam Wrench in the Works, NaoBun Project bekerja sama dengan LSM <a href=\"http://www.kontras.org/home/\">KontraS</a>. Lembaga ini bergerak dalam memperjuangkan hak-hak bagi orang hilang dan korban tindak kekerasan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46973\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46973\" data-attachment-id=\"46973\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ekshibisi-naobun-project-agensi-komik/attachment/05-naobun-project/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-naobun-project.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-naobun-project\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-naobun-project-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-naobun-project.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46973\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-naobun-project.jpg\" alt=\"05-naobun-project\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-naobun-project.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-naobun-project-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46973\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Tak hanya ekshibisi, NaoBun Project juga mengajak para pengunjung untuk terlibat dalam berbagai macam aktivitas di setiap hari pameran. Ada <em>portfolio review </em>bersama Bonni Rambatan dan Naomi Saddhadhika; seminar IP bersama kepala Legal &amp; IP Officer Fallisa Putri; serta <em>talkshow</em> bersama Bonni dan komikus Aisah PL tentang komik Sofia.</p>\n<p>Pengunjung juga bisa belajar lewat kelas menulis bersama Keinesasih Puteri dan Kathrinna Rakhmavika; atau kelas menggambar bersama Kathrinna, Jasmine Surkatty, Wulan Hastungkara, Nin Dianda, Soyatu, Xora, Sarah Puspaherning, dan Yustina Antonio. Aktivitas ini terbuka bagi siapa saja, termasuk anak-anak hingga dewasa.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46974\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46974\" data-attachment-id=\"46974\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ekshibisi-naobun-project-agensi-komik/attachment/06-naobun-project/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-naobun-project.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-naobun-project\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-naobun-project-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-naobun-project.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46974\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-naobun-project.jpg\" alt=\"06-naobun-project\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-naobun-project.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-naobun-project-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46974\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Kehadiran NaoBun Project tentunya menambah semarak dunia komik Indonesia. Ini pun menjadi kabar baik bagi para kreator, entah itu komikus atau penulis cerita. Kini ada banyak jalan yang bisa dipilih untuk menerbitkan karya komik, salah satunya adalah dengan bantuan NaoBun Project dan agensi komik lainnya. Pertanyaannya sekarang adalah, kalau sudah ada organisasi yang siap membantu menerbitkan komik kamu, apakah kamu juga sidah siap untuk menempa <em>skill</em> dan mental kamu sebagai kreator teladan?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"b04e5ffc-5253-55a7-9558-aca00b882cd8"}}}